thread.title: Monica Egan

author: Monica Egan
title: Monica Egan
text: As soon as we walked in the door, we were very impressed by the professionalism and friendliness of the staff and management at ServCorp Docklands. Now we are permanent clients on the floor here at 710 Collins Street, we could not be happier with the service we receive daily for both ourselves and our clients. It makes the biggest difference. Coming to work here is a pleasure and we cannot recommend ServCorp enough.
